            string input = "";
            int result = 0;

            for (int i = 0; i < input.Length - 14; i++)

                                                                if (CheckNonMatch(i + 12, 2, input))
                                                                    {
                                                                        result = i + 14;
                                                                        break;

            }

        public static bool CheckNonMatch(int start, int counter, string input)
        {
            for (int i = 1; i < counter; i++)
            {
                if (input[start] == input[start + i])
                {
                    return false;
                }
            }
            return true;
        }
